summary: This script creates a "deps" directory, changes to the "MiraiGo-Template" directory, sets GOPATH and GOPROXY environment variables for Go build commands, and then builds the project using "go build".

details.comment: This script creates a "deps" directory, changes to the "MiraiGo-Template" directory, sets GOPATH and GOPROXY environment variables for Go build commands, and then builds the project using "go build".
details.content:
#!/bin/bash
mkdir deps
cd MiraiGo-Template
GOPATH=$PWD/../deps GOPROXY=https://goproxy.cn,direct go build
